title: GET_HELI_GAS_TANK_HEALTH
content:
0xD4EC7858// GetHeliGasTankHealth
int GET_HELI_GAS_TANK_HEALTH(Vehicle heli);Parameters:heli: The helicopter to checkReturns: Returns the current health of the helicopter's gas tank.Note This native will always return 1000.0 unless SET_VEHICLE_BODY_HEALTH, SET_VEHICLE_ENGINE_HEALTH, or SET_VEHICLE_PETROL_TANK_HEALTH have been called with a value greater than 1000.0.
